ABOUT US

Mobile Auto Repair That Comes To You

With over 15 years of combined experience, Guerrero Mobile Mechanics started on January 1, 2022. Founded by Harmony Family LLC, we bring expert automotive repair directly to you. We operate as a mechanic dispatching company. Our mobile mechanics come ready to diagnose and repair your vehicle on-site. We save you time, money, and the trouble of towing. We promise quality service for urgent repairs and routine maintenance, wherever you are.

More About Us

Ensure your vehicle operates without issues by using our comprehensive maintenance services. From oil changes to engine diagnostics, we've got you covered.

Frequently Asked Questions

1. What services do you offer?

We offer tire services, alignments, oil changes, brake repairs, engine diagnostics, and a wide selection of quality rims.

2. Do I need to make an appointment?

Appointments are recommended.

3. How long will my service take?

Most services take between 30 minutes to an hour, depending on the job.

4. What brands of tires do you carry?

We carry top brands like Michelin, Goodyear, Bridgestone, and more.

5. Do you offer warranties on repairs?

Yes, all repairs and parts come with a 30 Days warranty. Ask for details during your diagnostics.

6. What payment methods do you accept?

We accept credit cards, debit cards, and cashapp.
